![](http://ootput.files.wordpress.com/2010/03/images.jpg?w=150 "images")

DD-WRT uses [inadyn](http://www.inatech.eu/inadyn/), and the settings for [DNS-o-matic](http://www.dnsomatic.com) are:{% codeblock %}

DDNS Service: Custom
DYNDNS Server: updates.dnsomatic.com
Username:
Password:
Hostname: all.dnsomatic.com
URL: /nic/update?{% endcodeblock %}
